data.description: Beautiful Ranch home in Ruskin Hills subdivision.  Curb Appeal indeed!  Upon entry a lush garden filled with Zinnias, Lilies, Sugar Baby Watermelons and treed landscaping with bird bath awaits you.  Front room boasts bay window that offers tons of natural light.  Hall bath has been remodeled and includes a new vanity and new fixtures. Fireplace in master bedroom adds that perfect ambiance...it includes a gas insert that is controlled with a remote. Expansive backyard presents an opportunity for outdoor relaxation and entertainment. Productive garden in place including potatoes, green beans, yellow corn, tomatoes and celery...you can continue to grow and enjoy your own delicious food.  Shed onsite for storage.   Easy access to local amenities  and transportation while providing a peaceful sanctuary to call home.  Don't miss out on this gem!
